name: NMIXX Sullyoon
description:
Please consider to support me by buying me some coffee so I can make a new LoRA faster. I do open commissions there too if you want to make your own custom LoRA: My BMAC page

There is v1B and v1C which is better than v1A here: v1B & v1C

Don't forget to include trigger word: nmixxsullyoon

Join KPOP Diffusion Discord: https://discord.gg/NrBDMX79Da

Best checkpoints/models to use:
Realistic: VisionGen, ChillOutMix, ArtEros, Deliberate, WoopWoop Photo
Fanart/painting style: Dreamshaper, LucidMix, SunshineMix

Use it wisely. I don't responsible for anything you generated with this LoRa.

Please don't put any NSFW generated images on the reviews or you will get banned by Civitai moderators.
